== Build requirements ==

* TeXLive 2015 distribution: https://www.tug.org/texlive/
* The list of required TeX packages include Cyrillic language support, XeLaTeX, Tikz, Bibtex.
  Bibliography generated by combination of Biblatex, Biber, biblatex-gost works, but initials are broken by TeXLive 2015
  for unknown reason. TL 2013 was OK.
* GNU `make`

Build works on Linux. It also works on Windows, provided there is a GNU Make.

== Build instructions ==

To build the Web version, run `make` inside the `metoda` directory. The final document is called `main-web.pdf`.

